address.streetAddress: Cali Plan, Pebble Creek at River Landing

location.fullValue: Cali Plan, Pebble Creek at River Landing

data.description: Luxury Living-Cozy 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home with privacy fence. New lighting in living room, dining, kitchen, breakfast area. Pantry in Kitchen. New Paint, Hardwood Floors and Blinds throughout. Tile in Bathrooms. Accent wall in Dining Room and 2nd Bedroom/Office. Master Bath with Tile Shower and Garden Tub. Enclosed sunroom is great for pets. Extended concrete patio. Large sodded backyard. Sprinkler System. River Landing HOA amenities include resort style pool with separate kiddie pool, tennis courts, basketball court, playground, clubhouse with children's clubhouse, fitness center. Close to Trash Panda Stadium, I565 and Redstone Arsenal.
